cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.COMM, cs.SY, cs.MM

This paper discusses the coexistence of different waveforms in 5G networks, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), communication systems (cs.COMM), system engineering (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM). However, the focus on waveform design and interference analysis suggests that cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely categories, followed by cs.COMM, cs.SY, and cs.MM.
